225032_2c5cb87e1d5b576d5a3a71310d8e8e33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225032_2c5cb87e1d5b576d5a3a71310d8e8e33.jpg&h=7e6b4eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n置業POST 係時候加入林太敬拜環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/225238_c2e09a7b5958bf79ab615df3c9244a48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225238_c2e09a7b5958bf79ab615df3c9244a48.jpg&h=1429f73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重溫經典<br />\n林太豪氣回應，「290萬已經最低，我個仔買貴40萬冇咩問題，佢要住㗎嘛，如果升又點呢。阿仔買嘅單位，銀行估到價，銀行唔會死錯人嘅，嗰啲咁既專家，食屎啦！我哋唔係有見地，我哋係腳踏實地，唔聽專家㗎，聽專家意見就死啦。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170308/19950864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170308%2F19950864&d=GoifjXAQR2dURKEittJIZfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=85b96624\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170308%2F19950864&h=1154b792\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170308/19950864</a><br />\n<br />\n幾時係買樓時機？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/225031_b0f1496fd73d036205628c24b24bb772.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225031_b0f1496fd73d036205628c24b24bb772.png&h=d72727b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/225031_090360ff0b029b1f57ca40fe2926c68a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225031_090360ff0b029b1f57ca40fe2926c68a.png&h=54ca4a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n立此存照, 置業POST 巴絲打同股榮對賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n金管局有一個圖，不妨可借用供大家參考。該局根據差估處及統計處收集數據，以一個約500多呎單位的置業成本及租賃成本計算出買租價差比率，今年上半年比率達到176%，反映樓宇買家置業成本較租樓多出76%，1998年有關比率於300%以上見頂，然後急跌。2008年有關比率升至150%水平後，亦見頂急回。<br />\n過去兩年一直提示樓市有下跌風險，最終樓價指數反而升逾兩成。2018年預測，香港跟美國加息，樓價估計調整兩成，如明年底CCL最終不低於135（現為182.17），此欄及fb再不會再談任何樓市的相關資訊。<br />\n<br />\n股榮<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stockwing1/posts/788073491376493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstockwing1%2Fposts%2F788073491376493&d=GoifjXAQR2dURKEittJIZfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=b5471f42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stockwing1/posts/788073491376493</a><br />\n<br />\n最新2018/05/04公佈, 中原城市領先指數182.17 比上週上升1.6%"},{"pid":"7b6d117256cd33dc645fbbfc00762badf2acc559","tid":659916,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"爆post冇人開我頂住先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d8cbb8f29342f13e6f1888c806f0d0cc21eb0c","tid":659916,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"上一期post<br />\n<br />\n【水煮意粉樂趣多】低調置業討論區（160）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/657352/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/657352/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e226d9e7c7cef7e9633f39e52cd98eab284f1a82","tid":659916,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00d8cbb8f29342f13e6f1888c806f0d0cc21eb0c","tid":659916,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"上一期post<br />\n<br />\n【水煮意粉樂趣多】低調置業討論區（160）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/657352/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/657352/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac